      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-010 Define Supplier Standards</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-AFC25326-4F05-41F5-9EA0-DE9E9C41E8D6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="true" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="true" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Specs stored in Doc Locator. Example of specifications -
*Supplier Selection Process Specification  (DL-0002375.pdf),
*Supply Chain Supplier Qualification (DL-0002403.pdf)
*Supplier Segmentation Governing Spec (DL-0002460.pdf)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A02C91FF-89EC-44A5-9BF3-CA622B99CC8C" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="true" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="true" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Includes all SCQATS (Safety, Cost, Quality, Availability, Technology, and Sustainability) specs and policies</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-80F85C75-9718-464D-858D-93A273AF8E10" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
